high_descs: Turn around and walk to the microwave.
Take the apple out of the microwave.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Place the apple back in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Place a washed apple in a microwave.

high_descs: Turn around, head to the microwave on the counter.
Take the apple out of the microwave.
Bring the apple to the sink on the right.
Wash the apple in the sink.
Bring the cleaned apple to the microwave on the left.
Put the cleaned apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, take out the apple from inside, then close it.
Turn right to face the sink.
Clean the apple in the sink.
Turn left to face the microwave
Open the microwave, put the apple inside, then close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean apple in the microwave.
